This file lists the channel op flags recognised by the core, or by existing modules.

Core:

on: Default op flags. Includes all flags marked with a (D).

ban (D): Set/remove bans, disconnect users.
invite (D): Invite users with op privileges.
restrict (D): Set (un)restrict modes on the channel.
msg (D): Override restrictions on messaging the channel.
topic (D): Override restrictions on setting the topic.
op (D): Op/deop users.
mark (D): Mark and unmark (inc. voice) users.
viewdata (D): View hidden channel data, such as ban exceptions and unrestricts.
viewflags (D): View chanop flags in the channel.
